{"title":"Hello Hexo 之 搭建教程","date":"2019-07-26T16:10:21.000Z","thumbnail":"/img/ByTheSea.jpeg","link":"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程","tags":["教程"],"updated":"2019-07-26T16:43:15.465Z","content":"<h2 id=\"HEXO介绍\">HEXO介绍<a href=\"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程#HEXO介绍\"></a></h2><p>官方主页点这里👉<a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo.io </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"安装HEXO\">安装HEXO<a href=\"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程#安装HEXO\"></a></h2><blockquote>\n<p>环境依赖 GitHub 以及 node.js</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>测试安装是否成功</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"部署HEXO\">部署HEXO<a href=\"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程#部署HEXO\"></a></h2><p>在合适的位置，创建一个文件夹，cd到该目录，执行:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>此时HEXO所需要的文件就已经生成在该目录，通过执行如下命令生成静态页面</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo generate //可缩写为 hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>执行如下命令本地测试</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"配置Github\">配置Github<a href=\"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程#配置Github\"></a></h2><p>这里建议参考👉<a href=\"https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/wiki/896043488029600\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">廖雪峰的Github教程</a><br>在项目中按照如下格式创建仓库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">username.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"安装远程部署插件hexo-deployer-git\">安装远程部署插件hexo-deployer-git<a href=\"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程#安装远程部署插件hexo-deployer-git\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>安装完成后，修改目录下的_config.yml</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: https://github.com/YourgithubName/YourgithubName.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>yml文件要注意缩进和空格</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"远程部署\">远程部署<a href=\"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程#远程部署\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo deploy // 可缩写为hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"修改主题\">修改主题<a href=\"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程#修改主题\"></a></h2><p>在Themes文件夹中添加主题，并在_config.yml文件中更改主题文件夹名字<br>例如:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">theme: inside</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>这里使用inside主题 ， 主题链接在这里👉<a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/theme-inside\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">theme-inside</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"绑定域名\">绑定域名<a href=\"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程#绑定域名\"></a></h2><p>在sourse文件夹中新建CNAME文件，其中填写你的域名</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>注意CNAME文件没有后缀</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>在Github的项目页，进入设置，设置项目域名。</p>\n<h2 id=\"注意事项\">注意事项<a href=\"post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程#注意事项\"></a></h2><p>在有内容更改时必须执行hexo g，如果出现问题，建议多检查一下yml文件的格式以及执行hexo clear命令</p>\n","prev":{"title":"裱物师","link":"post/裱物师"},"next":{"title":"PLSQL笔记","link":"post/PLSQL笔记"},"plink":"http://luer.cf/post/Hello-Hexo-之-搭建教程/","toc":[{"title":"HEXO介绍","id":"HEXO介绍","index":"1"},{"title":"安装HEXO","id":"安装HEXO","index":"2"},{"title":"部署HEXO","id":"部署HEXO","index":"3"},{"title":"配置Github","id":"配置Github","index":"4"},{"title":"安装远程部署插件hexo-deployer-git","id":"安装远程部署插件hexo-deployer-git","index":"5"},{"title":"远程部署","id":"远程部署","index":"6"},{"title":"修改主题","id":"修改主题","index":"7"},{"title":"绑定域名","id":"绑定域名","index":"8"},{"title":"注意事项","id":"注意事项","index":"9"}]}